These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-1::.
City: liverpool, london, san-francisco, miami, new-york, edinburgh
There are 6 different favourite colors: coral, orange, brown, white, black, turquise
House: modern, palace, townhouse, ranch-style, farmhouse, cottage
 1. the modern house is the person who likes brown##1
 2. the palace house is on the far right##1
 3. the modern house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the cottage house is the person who likes turquise##1
 5. the person who likes orange is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the palace house##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is the person who likes orange##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the farmhouse house and the person who likes orange##2
13. the modern house is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who likes black##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |     4      |    5     |     6      |
| City   | miami | new-york  | edinburgh  | liverpool | london  | san-francisco   |
| Color           | white | orange | turquise | black        | brown    | coral |
| House     | townhouse    | ranch-style     | cottage   | farmhouse       | modern | palace       |

