.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: singing, magic-tricks, collecting, rock-climbing, drawing, card-games
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, marigold, bellflower, dahlia, azalea
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, trike, taxi, boat, snowmobile, car
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the trike##1
13. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |    5     |     6      |
| Hobby      | collecting     | singing | magic-tricks     | rock-climbing    | drawing | card-games     |
| Flower   | daffodil | aconite | bellflower | azalea | marigold  | dahlia  |
| Transport           | trike    | taxi    | snowmobile     | car  | boat    | subway |

