.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, rat, goldfish, ferret, hedgehog
There 6 different types of food: potato, artichoke, apricot, tomato, mango, eggplant
There are 6 different nationalities: italian, brazilian, malaysian, dutch, polish, canadian
 1. the person eating mango is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 2. the polish is the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the brazilian is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
 8. the italian is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the canadian is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the owner of the ferret is between the person eating tomato and the polish##2
12. the italian is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |   6   |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | goat | ferret     | rat | goldfish | turtle |
| Food   | mango     | eggplant      | artichoke | tomato        | apricot     | potato |
| Nationality     | brazilian | polish     | malaysian   | italian          | dutch      | canadian |

