 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the journalist##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
 8. the person who growslily is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the analyst##1
10. the person who growstulip is the designer##1
11. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growstulip##2
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |    4     |     5      |    6    |
