 3. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the cain-smoker is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's sport is sailing and the blend-smoker##2
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
12. the baccarat-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |    3     |   4    |     5     |    6    |
| Birthday   | april | march       | january   | december    | may  | september |
