 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
