 4. the havana-smoker is the craftsman house##1
 5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 6. the cain-smoker is the ranch-style house##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the person playing bridge is between the game-smoker and the palace house##2
 9. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the wooden house is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
11. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the wooden house##1
12. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3      |     4      |     5     |    6    |
| House           | palace | ranch-style | futuristic | craftsman | wooden | townhouse |
| Cigar   | siglo     | cain           | game      | havana        | bolivar    | baccarat  |
| Game   | domino | bridge     | whist  | backgammon   | scrabble    | monopoly |

